HEADWORD: Tittup
<hw>Tit"tup</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of tittuping; lively, gay,
or restless behavior or gait; a prance or caper.</def> <altsp>[Written
also <asp>titup</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

